  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>quinoa</strong> to a pot with a matching lid with 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 10 min&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>green beans</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, finely chop or grate the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>\r\n<p>Zest the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and cut in half&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the&nbsp;<strong>chopped parsley</strong>&nbsp;and <strong>garlic</strong> to a&nbsp;<strong>pestle &amp; mortar</strong>&nbsp;with the&nbsp;<strong>capers</strong>, 2 tbsp&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>water&nbsp;</strong>and a pinch of&nbsp;<strong>salt</strong></p>\r\n<p>Grind to a paste, then add the juice of&nbsp;1/2&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong>,&nbsp;1 tbsp&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong>, the <strong>lemon zest</strong>&nbsp;and mix to combine &ndash; this is your <strong>lemon&nbsp;caper dressing</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 10 min, add the&nbsp;<strong>green beans</strong>&nbsp;to the quinoa pot with 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>water</strong> and cook, covered, for 10 min further or until all the <strong>water</strong> has absorbed and the<strong>&nbsp;quinoa&nbsp;</strong>and&nbsp;<strong>green beans</strong>&nbsp;are tender</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and leave to steam-dry, uncovered, until serving</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Pat the&nbsp;<strong>mackerel fillets</strong> dry and season the skin with <strong>salt</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>mackerel</strong>, skin-side down and cook for 4 min</p>\r\n<p>Tip: hold the fillets down flat with a spatula to crisp up the <span class=\"text-highlight\">skin then</span> flip and cook for 1 min further</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the remaining <strong>lemon</strong>&nbsp;half into wedges</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>spinach</strong> to a large bowl with the cooked <strong>quinoa</strong>,<strong> green beans</strong> and half the&nbsp;<strong>caper and lemon dressing&nbsp;</strong>and give it a good mix up &ndash; this is your <strong>quinoa salad&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.--step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.--step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.--step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.--step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1470.--step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>mackerel fillets</strong> over the <strong>quinoa salad</strong></p>\r\n<p>Drizzle with the remaining <strong>dressing</strong> and garnish with the<strong> lemon wedges</strong></p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 8,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    }
